The address and cellphone number of Matt Theunissen, who posted racist comments on social media has been leaked to social media.Matt wrote: So no more sporting events for South Africa I ve never been more proud than to say our government are a bunch of K*****S yes, I said it so go and f**k yourselves you black f**king c**ts. He quickly deleted his post but it was too late because it had already been captured and went viral on all social media platforms. Hashtag #MattTheunissen saw more than 100 000 posts and comments in just few hours. It is believed that he was referring to Sports Minister, Fikile Mbalula&#8217;s decision to ban three sports codes from hosting international events. comments